},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maToirapN","text_ar":"مَطِْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] and thus it is mentioned [in the K] in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mTr","text_ar":"مطر"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n38701","headword_ar":"مَطْرَةٌ","root":"mTr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rain; a shower of rain"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A; and S, K, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magorapN","text_ar":"مَغْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTorapN mubaArakapN","text_ar":"مَطْرَةٌ مُبَارَكَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A blessed rain."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (A.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTarN","text_ar":"مَطَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTarapN","text_ar":"مَطَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n38702","headword_ar":"مَطَرَةٌ","root":"mTr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, Sgh, K, also mentioned in the L, on the authority of IAar, and in such a manner as implies that it may be also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTorapN","text_ar":"مَطْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skin of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirobap","text_ar":"قِرْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, &c.:) applied in the present day to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idaAwap","text_ar":"اـِدَاوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [I have found it now applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a large bottle of leather,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of wood:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amoTaArN","text_ar":"اَمْطَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["TA"]},{"entry_id":"n38703","headword_ar":"مَطِرَةٌ","root":"mTr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaTirN","text_ar":"عَطِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}